"{\"uid\": \"ealingtimes.co.uk-news-24432888.cunningham-using-self-belief-fuel-maiden-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Sport Caden Cunningham admits that when he steps onto the mat to face taekwondo heavyweights who are half a foot taller than him, a little trepidation goes through his mind.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13, \"end\": 23, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9951037477417275, \"rank\": 0.00467119154303306, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mat\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 61}, {\"ngram\": \"taekwondo heavyweights\", \"from\": 70, \"to\": 92}, {\"ngram\": \"a little trepidation\", \"from\": 130, \"to\": 150}, {\"ngram\": \"his mind\", \"from\": 164, \"to\": 172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, the 21-year-old from Huddersfield reminds himself that he is more than capable of achieving his aim of becoming the youngest Olympic heavyweight champion in his sport and goes out there to kick them in the face.\", \"from\": 176, \"to\": 393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 203, \"end\": 215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huddersfield\", \"score\": 0.8685538454860646, \"rank\": 0.15117323811096467, \"text\": \"Huddersfield\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huddersfield\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huddersfield\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his aim\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 281}, {\"ngram\": \"the youngest Olympic heavyweight champion\", \"from\": 294, \"to\": 335}, {\"ngram\": \"his sport\", \"from\": 339, \"to\": 348}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 392}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You need a certain level of confidence to succeed in a sport where kicks to the head are not only allowed but encouraged, and Cunningham is planning to use that belief to fuel him to Olympic glory.\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 592, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 521, \"end\": 531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9951037477417275, \"rank\": 0.00467119154303306, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a certain level\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 419}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 433}, {\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 455}, {\"ngram\": \"kicks\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 467}, {\"ngram\": \"the head\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 479}, {\"ngram\": \"that belief\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 562}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic glory\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"You think 'Oh my god, oh my god, oh my god, he's massive!'\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 662, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then as soon as I get there, I put my headguard on, I get in the mindset of 'I am going to kick you in the face'.\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my headguard\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 710}, {\"ngram\": \"the mindset\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 735}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 774}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me, it's about building an ego and pride when you get into the ring.\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 851, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an ego\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 813}, {\"ngram\": \"pride\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 823}, {\"ngram\": \"the ring\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 850}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A lot of these guys are bigger and older than me.\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 901, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"these guys\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not small, but I am not a big heavyweight.\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 949, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big heavyweight\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 948}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of these have five or six inches on me, and ten years' experience.\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 1021, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"five or six inches\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 987}, {\"ngram\": \"ten years' experience\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So most fights I am the underdog and I go out there and think, I will kick you in the face, let us get it on.\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the underdog\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1054}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1112}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For anyone to go to the Olympics and not go for gold, you should hold yourself to a higher standard.\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1144}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1166}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1186}, {\"ngram\": \"a higher standard\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1233}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You almost want to manifest it, speak it into existence.\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1291, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"existence\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1290}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But also, I decided I was going to go to these Olympics ten years ago, I did not decide I was going to go to participate, I am going to win.\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1432, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these Olympics\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This Olympics is an opportunity to fight the best I can in front of the most people.\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1519, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This Olympics\", \"f